metadata.name: The Lights, The Eyes
metadata.description:
"Dear diary, 

I just received a picture that a friend of mine used magic to appear on it.

Unbelievable, it is so different from the painting I used to see on the wall. It looks more realistic, she can even capture the light in it. What a magical tool.

Maybe I will ask her to take more for me. Does it sound too greedy?"
